*Ražanj* je bio veoma važan za izvođenje operacija u *ratu* (The siege was very important for conducting operations in the war).

*Ratnici* su bili obučeni da se bore u *ratu* (The warriors were trained to fight in the war). 

Svi su se čudili hrabrosti i odlučnosti *ratnika* u *ratu* (Everyone was amazed by the courage and determination of the warriors in the war).

Kako bi se sprečilo da *rat* postane beskonačan, postoje međunarodni sporazumi (In order to prevent the war from becoming endless, there are international agreements).